projects.title: Philips Sonicare For Kids - Universal (iPhone+iPad) Application
projects.description:
Philips Sonicare For Kids

Transform brush time into fun time! Watch as your kids engage and learn with Sparkly. No more asking them if they have brushed or for how long.

98% of parents surveyed say it’s easier to get their kids to brush longer and better*

Meet Sparkly! A furry, friendly creature with a big smile who needs your help battling bacteria bugs! Brush your Sparkly’s teeth using the Sonicare for Kids Bluetooth connected toothbrush and you’ll win presents and new features. Along the way you’ll learn better brushing techniques, get healthy food tips, and receive awards for consistent brushing.

For Parents:
•	Gets kids excited to brush
•	Establishes healthy tooth brushing habits for life
•	Teaches correct brushing techniques, as recommended by dentists
•	Allows you to monitor and track your kids’ brushing habits via the parent dashboard
•	Lets you set brushing reminders for your kids

For Kids:
•	Learn healthy habits right along with Sparkly!
•	Toothbrush syncs with the app for real-time fun
•	Receive presents and awards for continuous brushing
•	Brush time = fun time!

Compatibility:
•	Compatible with the use of any toothbrush
•	Some features are only accessible with the use of the Philips Sonicare for Kids rechargeable toothbrush enabled with Bluetooth® wireless technology

projects.title: Us Likey Social Networking - iPhone Application
projects.description:
Us Likey
Us Likey is place where you can create and share your personalized collection focused ONLY on the specific consumer products, places, styles, brands, foods, gadgets, music, movies, hobbies and everything else that defines you. Share all the specific details about your personal preferences – everything from your favorite brand + flavor of ice cream or favorite restaurant or the type of perfume you wear! 

FEATURES: 
•Discover, organize and save things to your Me Likey collection.
•Save, upload, and post images from the integrated camera or use the app’s browser to fetch images from your favorite sites to add to your Me Likey collection.
•Use photo filters to create cool, unique and vibrant posts.
•Discover new products, places, brands, styles, etc. 
through #hashtags and our Discover feature.
•Have fun sharing and sending recommendations to friends.
•Share all the specifics of what you like, want, buy and discover.
•Connect with friends using your contact list or social media.
•Facebook integration to share your posts.

projects.title: Saddlite by ThoroVet! - iPad Application
projects.description:
Saddlite is the first truly mobile equine practice software system designed for equine veterinarians. 

Saddlite is more than an app, it is a subscription-based software system designed to streamline your clinic’s administrative work as well as veterinary work in the field. The app features a built-in, fully customizable SOAP process. Saddlite also syncs all data in real time between the iPad app and the office, and can be accessed 24/7 through the app or the web based program for office administrators. Track billing, patient info, exam notes, treatments, history, medications, labs, diagnostics, images, and much more. Customize the plan screen to meet the needs of your practice - with your specific medications, treatments, procedures, and pricing. Generate invoices on-the-go, right from your iPad. Saddlite gives you complete control of your business on the iPad, so that everything you need to know about every horse is with you 24/7. Stores and backs up all data in the cloud – no hard drive space required and no hardware requirements. All you need is an iPad to get your practice on-board with the revolution in equine veterinary practice – Saddlite by ThoroVet!
